metadata.name: Juniper & Rinta : Chroma
metadata.description:
Welcome to The Grandeur, to the other. 

Where the stars dance and twirl, to a melancholy dirge, and the sky is partners with the chroma. A world, perhaps terribly dark, but beautiful in its dread.  Let us embrace this alternate universe, and allow our minds to run wild.  
For in this place, there are no limits or boundaries--only endless possibility. 

Welcome and be still. Intend.
